natural_language: The system will install updates, except if there is not enough disk space or the update is not available.
ground_truth: SOFTWARE_INSTALL IF ENOUGH_DISK_SPACE AND UPDATE_AVAILABLE

natural_language: The application will launch, except if the operating system is outdated or the user is not logged in.
ground_truth: APPLICATION_LAUNCH IF OPERATING_SYSTEM_UPDATED AND USER_LOGGED_IN

natural_language: The feature will be enabled, except when the user is not authenticated or the feature is not available.
ground_truth: FEATURE_ENABLED IF USER_AUTHENTICATED AND FEATURE_AVAILABLE

natural_language: The service will start automatically, except if manual mode is selected or the service is not configured.
ground_truth: SERVICE_START IF AUTO_MODE_SELECTED AND SERVICE_CONFIGURED

natural_language: The device will enter sleep mode, except before 5 minutes of inactivity or when the device is not idle.
ground_truth: SLEEP_MODE IF INACTIVITY_5MIN AND DEVICE_IDLE

natural_language: Notifications will appear, except when do not disturb mode is active or when the phone is switched off.
ground_truth: NOTIFICATIONS IF DND_MODE_DISABLED AND PHONE_ON

natural_language: The backup will proceed, except if the storage device is not connected or backup is not enabled.

ground_truth: SYSTEM_REBOOT IF PROCESSES_COMPLETED AND REBOOT_REQUESTED
